title: Locked Behind The Doors- Persian Underground Music
description:
A Collection of iranian rock, Electronic, Alternative and Fusion Music. 
This is not something you can find Easily any other way. 

Politically Banned And Barred From Iranian official Music Scene, These Folks Decided To Walk All over it and either Released their works for free on Net or kept their Focus On Iranian Market Living Outside of Iran. 
Which by its own means is kinda crowded enough to make their gigs possible every now and then. 

IF YOU CAN BUY THEIR ALBUMS//HESITATE NO MORE AND DO SO 
INTENDED ONLY FOR THOSE WHO CANT PURCHASE THE WORKS




Collected By Parham __ PerSlash.
